                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City police-constable No.</hi> 477.) I produce a certificate of the prisoner's conviction, which I got at Mr. Clark's office—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted on</hi> 27<hi rend="italic">th Feb.</hi>, 6<hi rend="italic">th Vict., and imprisoned six months</hi>)—the prisoner is the person.</p>
